{"tid":1567521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾鈺成是我們最堅實的後盾","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:23:24.000Z","uid":213969,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1045c681257f23fe111b5ad86438f0c18474264e","tid":1567521,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[member]當日不塗污他的油像<br />\n正是因為義士們知道他是朋友<br />\n一直帶領 提醒著年輕一代<br />\n<br />\n今日更對國歌作出極高評價<br />\n<blockquote>近日在多個場合都有大批市民齊唱反修例歌曲《願榮光歸香港》，立法會前主席曾鈺成表示，這首歌他有聽過，被問到歌詞是否有港獨意味，他表示不想評論歌曲的含意，讚揚歌曲的技巧和質素相當高，相信是出自專業人士之手。</blockquote><br />\n但看到有人把他當作敵人<br />\n真的心痛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他可是陳永仁<br />\n是我們的朋友 義士 領袖<br />\n<br />\n對於運動發展可謂是盡心盡力<br />\n更多的事跡 我就不再詳述了<br />\n只要是兄弟就明白 <br />\n必須忠實追隨他 學習他<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他的讚賞激勵我們<br />\n堅持就對了<br />\n[/member］"},{"pid":"1ad2b4db090838a7ceb3b836209d0b8b45cb6885","tid":1567521,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街了"},{"pid":"544639564e8c184f48e063b4278665d022051d65","tid":1567521,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"老鼠曾=根正苗紅共產黨"},{"pid":"d8ee3d410513d3c126ebd52edc495e51136e6a9c","tid":1567521,"uid":213969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"544639564e8c184f48e063b4278665d022051d65","tid":1567521,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"老鼠曾=根正苗紅共產黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"是<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b582158fee10c26c92ac4d3933691c940c84f7c","tid":1567521,"uid":213969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"中共是敵人 <br />\n